<h1 class="h3 mb-4 text-gray-800">Setup 2FA</h1>

<div class="card shadow mb-4">
  <div class="card-header py-3 d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
    <h6 class="m-0 font-weight-bold text-primary">Google Authenticator</h6>
  </div>

  <div class="card-body">
    <div class="alert alert-info">
      Akun kamu belum mengaktifkan 2FA. Scan QR ini pakai aplikasi Google Authenticator, lalu masukkan kode 6 digit untuk aktivasi.
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4 text-center mb-3">
        <div class="border rounded p-2 bg-white">
          <div id="setup-twofa-qr-canvas" style="display:none; min-height:240px; align-items:center; justify-content:center;"></div>
          <img id="setup-twofa-qr" src="" alt="QR" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; display:none;" />
          <div id="setup-twofa-qr-placeholder" class="text-muted" style="min-height:240px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;">
            QR belum dibuat
          </div>
        </div>

        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm mt-2" id="setup-btn-generate-2fa">
          Generate QR
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Secret (manual)</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="setup-twofa-secret" readonly>
          <small class="form-text text-muted">Kalau QR gagal discan, input secret ini manual di Google Authenticator.</small>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Kode 6 digit</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="setup-twofa-code" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="6" placeholder="123456">
        </div>

        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="setup-btn-verify-2fa">
          Verifikasi & Aktifkan
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

